<%= stylesheet_link_tag "modals" %>
<script>
  $(document).click(function (e) {
      var companion = $('#shareCompanionModal');

      //if the target of the click isn't the modal...
      if (!companion.is(e.target)&& companion.has(e.target).length === 0) { companion.modal('hide'); }
  });
</script>

<div id="shareCompanionModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="shareCompanionModal" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="explore-container">
    <h4 id ="title">
      Now download the Mobile Companion App to pay and get paid via <a target="_blank" href="https://stripe.com/gallery">
        <span id ="secure">QR Code Scanning powered by Stripe.</span></a>
      </br>
    </br>
        <span> Here's how it works, please read carefully!</span>
    </h4>
    <div class="app-info">
      <div class="app-preview">
        <iframe style="transform: scale(0.6)" width="438" height="930" src="//invis.io/AG67B4LCV" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="app-descriptions">
        <ul>
          <li id="app-title"><span>&#8592; </span>Try out the preview!</li>
          <li><span class="star">&#x2756;</span> When you meet the other party to exchange the item/service, have the Companion App ready and select the appropriate transaction. </li>
          <li><span class="star">&#x2756;</span> If you are paying, have your QR code scanner open and simply scan the QR code on the other person's phone. That's it! No cash needed.</li>
          <li><span class="star">&#x2756;</span> If you are being paid, open the QR code page in the app, and simply have it scanned. Your Adae Account will be credited instantly.</li>
          <li><span class="star">&#x2756;</span> If the item needs to be returned or if a service is being offered, you will need to scan again at the end of the transaction.</li>
        </ul>
        <div id="follow"> Got it? Follow the links below!</div>
        <a target="_blank" href="https://itunes.apple.com/ca/app/adae/id1084039853?mt=8"><%= image_tag "modal_app_store.png", class: "modal_app_store" %></a>
        <a target="_blank" href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.adae.justinelee.adaecompanion&hl=en"><%= image_tag "modal_play_store.png", class: "modal_play_store" %></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
